    <metadata>
      <schema>http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM</schema>
      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">
        <general>
          <identifier>
            <catalog>oercommons.org</catalog>
            <entry>1770206431</entry>
          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">Hall of Presidents</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Hall der Präsidenten</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Hall des présidents</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Salão dos presidentes</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Corridoio dei presidenti</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αίθουσα των Προέδρων</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Pasillo de presidentes</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">offers a selection of portraits of U.S. presidents. Each portrait is accompanied by a brief description of the president and his accomplishments.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">bietet eine Auswahl der Portraits der VEREINIGTE 
STAATEN Präsidenten an. Jedes Portrait wird von einer kurzen 
Beschreibung des Präsidenten und seiner Vollendungen begleitet.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">offre une sélection des verticales des 
présidents des ETATS-UNIS. Chaque verticale est accompagnée 
d'une courte description du président et de ses accomplissements.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">oferece uma seleção dos retratos de presidentes 
de ESTADOS UNIDOS. Cada retrato é acompanhado por uma 
descrição breve do presidente e de suas realizações.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">offre una selezione dei ritratti dei presidenti
degli STATI UNITI. Ogni ritratto è accompagnato da una 
descrizione sommaria del presidente e delle sue realizzazioni.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">προσφέρει μια επιλογή των πορτρέτων των ΑΜΕΡΙΚΑΝΙΚΩΝ 
Προέδρων. Κάθε πορτρέτο συνοδεύεται από μια συνοπτική 
περιγραφή του Προέδρου και των ολοκληρώσεών του.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">ofrece una selección de retratos de los 
presidentes de ESTADOS UNIDOS. Cada retrato es acompañado por 
una descripción abreviada del presidente y de sus realizaciones.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Sciences Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Ciências Sociais</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Scienze Sociali</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Κοινωνικές επιστήμες</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Ciencias Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
